LONG DESC: The Bedroom was continuously used to host guests, and it can be seen in the wear and tear of this room. The history in here feels rich since travelers near and far have left their mark in some way on this room, mostly by peeling wallpaper or writing in the guest book. The furniture layout is minimal in this room, and  From here, the exits are on the south wall to the Closet and east wall to the 2nd Floor Hallway.
